  * Bumped to 0.2beta

2002-07-29 (jurgenv@cwi.nl)
  * Changed configuration option --with-xml to --with-libxml2 to
    conform with autobundle
  * Delayed calling xml2-config to build time 
  * Re-released 0.1 (just enhanced configuration, no new functionality)

2002-07-24 (jurgenv@cwi.nl)
  * Made aterm2xml compliant with Meta-Environment commandline interface
  * Made xml2aterm compliant with Meta-Environment commandline interface
  * Release 0.1

