  * Put aterm-xml in the CVS repository

2002-05-01 (kasperh@science.uva.nl)
  * rewrote some functions to make better use of the ATerm
    library.

2002-03-01 (jurgenv@cwi.nl)
  * added --with-xml option. If config-xml is your PATH
    the configure scripts finds out automatically where the xml
    library is. If if it is not in your PATH you need to set
    it using --with-xml=path/to/xml/directory
  * added --with-aterm option.
  * added tests

2002-03-01 (kasperh@science.uva.nl)
